<li><a href="http://www.northeastchp.org/nac/businesses/refrigeration.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.northeastchp.org/nac/businesses/refrigeration.htm" rel="nofollow">Thermally-Activated Machines Refrigeration Cycle</a>: Northeast CHP Application Center at the University of Massachusetts Amherst and Pace University</li>
</ul>


